snippet.textDisplay:
I am an atheist but I respect all the religions and faiths of people. I felt let down at 6:48 "Gokul dekha, Mathura dekha ... Par tosa nah koi rang dekha re". It sounds like a comparison of religions and corresponding Gods.

One can pray to the God he/she believes in; without comparing (undermining) the God of other religion. Irrespective of what one believes in, one should respect all other religions. #Humanity
